<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/html">
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type'/>
</head>
<body>

Emails this would have been sent to:
<ul>
<% @emails.each do |email| %>
  <li><%= email %></li>
<% end %>
</ul>

Build Part for <%= @build_part.project.name %> failed<br>
<br>
Go to <%= project_build_part_url(@build_part.build_instance.project, @build_part.build_instance, @build_part) %> for details<br>
<br>
Or go directly to <%= link_to("stdout.tar.gz", @stdout_url) %>

<h1>Changes since last success</h1>
<% @git_changes.each do |git_change| %>
  <b>commit <%= link_to(git_change[:hash], "#{@build_part.project.repository.base_html_url}/commit/#{git_change[:hash]}") %></b><br>
  Author: <%= git_change[:author] %><br>
  Date: <%=  git_change[:date] %><br>
  <br>
  <%= git_change[:message] %>
  <br><br>
<% end %>

</body>
</html>